# DCS

Code generator into a data-oriented architecture for high-performance runtime.

```
|---------------------------------------|
|                Context                |
|---------------------------------------|
| Components[] | Systems[] | Contexts[] |
|---------------------------------------|
```

```
|---------------------------------------|
|        Lifecycle Context Systems      |
|---------------------------------------|
| Init Systems[]                        |
|---------------------------------------|
| Loop Systems[][]                      |
|---------------------------------------|
| Exit Systems[]                        |
|---------------------------------------|
```

```
|---------------------------------------|
|             Component (SOA)           |
|-------------------|-------------------|
|      Capacity     |       Size        |
|-------------------|-------------------|
| Personal Fileds[]                     |
|---------------------------------------|
| Effects Fields[]                      |
|---------------------------------------|
| Overall Fields[]                      |
|---------------------------------------|
```

```bash
dune build
dune exec dcs
```

